# 3. Lineage Diagram (Skunk → Goblin → Bogey)

Skunk (automation, inference, auto‑download)  
  ↓ removed automation, added determinism  
Goblin (deterministic, no network, no magic)  
  ↓ added explicit acquisition + observability  
Bogey (deterministic + explicit user‑driven acquisition + exposure subsystem)

